      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in showroom condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every aspect, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, has been meticulously maintained to meet the most exacting standards. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a premier asset that delivers an uncompromising driving experience and remains in peak mechanical order. Serious inquiries are invited to inspect this exceptional example of engineering excellence.",
