    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, showroom-quality vehicle that satisfies even the most discerning collector. This car has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment, and it shows. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster with a professional ceramic coating applied to protect the finish; you will find no rock chips, swirl marks, or door dings anywhere on the body. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule. The premium leather upholstery remains supple and matte, free from any bolster wear or UV fading, and still carries that distinct 'new car' aroma. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the ambient lighting, functions exactly as it did the day it left the factory. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach. It features a full, documented service history from authorized specialists, with a recent major service including all fluid flushes and a comprehensive multi-point inspection. The undercarriage is as clean as the topside, showing no signs of corrosion or road grime. Riding on fresh, high-performance tires with 95% tread remaining, this vehicle offers a tight, responsive driving experience that is indistinguishable from a brand-new model. This is a rare opportunity to own a flawlessly preserved example of automotive excellence.",
